What you need to know:

Gor Mahia Secretary General Sam Ochola said Vaz Pinto who holds Uefa Pro and Caf 'A' coaching licence will hit the ground running upon arrivalIt's still not clear why Posta Rangers coach Sammy 'Pamzo' Omollo - who led Gor in Caf Champions League matches against APR of Rwanda and CR Belouizdad of Algeria - was not considered for the jobIt remains to be seen who the club will name as assistant coach after Patrick Odhiambo left K'Ogalo for a similar role at Bandari this week